    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">This Sustainable and Safe Event Management short course will help you to develop knowledge and understanding about the practical implementation of both sustainable development policies and health and safety principles for those working in the event industries. </span></p>
<p>The first half of the course focuses on the topic of sustainable event management while the second half focuses on managing health and safety at events.</p>
<p>NB There are no upcoming dates for this short course, but new dates may be added in due course. We can also run our short courses 'on demand' for organisations who would like to use them as part of staff development. <a href="mailto:%20ILO@qmu.ac.uk">Contact us</a> for more details about costs and how to arrange a bespoke delivery of this course.</p>
<p><a href="https://app.geckoform.com/public/#/modern/21FO00yts7rpi900abv6cjpubm" data-anchor="#/modern/21FO00yts7rpi900abv6cjpubm"><span class="blue-btn">Register your interest</span></a></p>]]></Value>
